article.linkText: Manon, Gray have 16, Cornell defeats Brown 84-83
article.story: PROVIDENCE, R.I. -- — Chris Manon and Isaiah Gray both had 16 points in Cornell's 84-83 victory against Brown on Saturday. Manon also contributed nine rebounds and four steals for the Big Red (13-3, 3-0 Ivy League). Gray shot 7 of 8 from the field. Keller Boothby was 4 of 7 shooting, including 2 for 5 from 3-point range, and went 3 for 3 from the line to finish with 13 points. Nana Owusu-Anane finished with 21 points, seven rebounds and four steals for the Bears (5-13, 1-2). Kino Lilly Jr. added 16 points and five assists for Brown. Felix Kloman also had 13 points and two steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
